{
  "texts": [
    "LEAP also enables educators to provide individualized feedback without technical expertise, making AI tools accessible to more teachers.",
    "The system allows educators to develop more effective learning interventions with targeted, pre-trained AI tasks, improving the precision and relevance of feedback.",
    "Overall, LEAP has the potential to revolutionize the way feedback is provided in education, making it more efficient, effective, and accessible, particularly in under-resourced institutions where personalized feedback is often needed but exceeds teaching staff capacity.",
    "We provide a detailed method of how specific prompts to the LLM can yield researchbased formative feedback, thereby bolstering various learning mechanisms to promote SRL.",
    "LEAP offers educators the flexibility to tailor these prompts to stimulate desired cognitive processes in students."
  ]
}